channel.name: The Vimeo HD Channel
channel.description:
Vimeo now supports HD in 1280x720! To create: upload a 1280x720 video and it will automatically convert to High Definition. If you have an older computer,
 let the video buffer before watching. Read the FAQ at http://vimeo.com/help/faq/hd.

This channel is moderated by the Vimeo Staff. If you want your HD video added to this channel,
 put a link in the shoutbox and we'll check it out.

channel.name: Time Lapse in HD
channel.description:
if it's a time lapse and presented in High Definition video (1280 by 720 or better),
 it will probably be shown here - thanks to all the great contributors out there :-)

If you have a time lapse video that you have created,
 and you would like to feature it on this channel?  Then post a link to your video in the channel "shout box" and we will check it out.

Oh,
 and if you like a video then don't forget to leave a comment and maybe click the 'LIKE' button - our contributors rely on your feedback and support...

be well ;-)
